OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,FControversial legislation that could
OL,7,Fallow terminally ill people to seek
OL,8,Fhelp to die begins its final stages at
OL,9,FHolyrood.
OL,11,FSome 328 amendments are to be debated
OL,12,Fby MSPs as part of stage three
OL,13,Fconsiderations of Liberal Democrat MSP
OL,14,FLiam McArthur's Assisted Dying for
OL,15,FTerminally Ill Adults (Scotland) Bill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,FThe large volume of amendments `
OL,7,Fcoupled with the nature of the
OL,8,Flegislation ` means the Scottish
OL,9,FParliament is expected to sit late
OL,10,Ftonight and again on Wednesday and
OL,11,FThursday as MSPs consider possible
OL,12,Fchanges.
OL,14,FThe Bill will then face a final vote
OL,15,Fat Holyrood in a week's time, on
OL,16,FTuesday March 17.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the start of stage
OL,7,Fthree considerations of the Bill, Mr
OL,8,FMcArthur urged MSPs not to "hunt for
OL,9,Fexcuses to kick the can down the road,
OL,10,Fas this issue is certainly not going
OL,11,Faway".
OL,13,FThe Liberal Democrat MSP insisted:
OL,14,F"This is the right Bill at the right
OL,15,Ftime. It's time to give terminally ill
OL,16,FScots that compassionate choice."
OL,26,@pD@\OUsD@EO]vD@AOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,FThe Bill, if passed, would allow
OL,7,Fterminally ill Scots to seek help to
OL,8,Fdie, with people needing to have two
OL,9,Fdoctors confirm both that they have a
OL,10,Fcondition which will kill them, and
OL,11,Fthat they have the mental capacity to
OL,12,Frequest an assisted death before being
OL,13,Feligible.
OL,15,FResearch by the National Centre for
OL,16,FSocial Research found that just over
OL,17,Ffour out five people in Scotland (81%)
OL,18,Fwant to see assisted dying introduced
OL,19,Ffor those diagnosed with a terminal
OL,20,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,FHowever, opponents of the Bill fear
OL,7,Fthat vulnerable people could be
OL,8,Fcoerced into ending their life.
OL,10,FMr McArthur said though that his
OL,11,Flegislation included "clear safeguards
OL,12,Fagainst coercion" based on "tried and
OL,13,Ftested" models already in place in
OL,14,Fcountries such as Australia and New
OL,15,FZealand.
OL,17,FThe MSP also stressed: "The new law
OL,18,Fcannot come into force until
OL,19,Fprotections for medical staff who wish
OL,20,Fnot to take part are enshrined in law."
OL,26,@sD@VOUtD@QO]tD@\OUuD@GO]yD@XOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,FHe added that MSPs could "add further
OL,7,Fprotections this week through
OL,8,Famendments" ` with these including a
OL,9,Fproposal backed by Mr McArthur setting
OL,10,Fout that someone must have six months
OL,11,Fto live or less to be eligible to seek
OL,12,Fan assisted death.
OL,14,FJeremy Balfour, an independent MSP for
OL,15,Fthe Lothians, said: "This debate has
OL,16,Funited MSPs from across the chamber `
OL,17,Fsome who don't even agree on a single
OL,18,Fother subject.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@KO]wD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,F"As a disabled person, I know very
OL,7,Fwell the risks not just of coercion,
OL,8,Fbut of how society views disabled
OL,9,Fpeople, and how we can feel like a
OL,10,Fburden.
OL,12,F"I'm fortunate in that I have a strong
OL,13,Fsupport network around me to protect
OL,14,Fme from those thoughts, processes and
OL,15,Foutside influences.
OL,17,F"But for those who don't, I am
OL,18,Fterrified for them and the impact the
OL,19,Fpassing of this dangerous Bill would
OL,20,Fhave."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,FAudrey Nicoll, SNP MSP for Aberdeen
OL,7,FSouth and North Kincardine, said:
OL,8,F"Many MSPs like me began this process
OL,9,Fsympathetic to need for a Bill of this
OL,10,Fnature to be fully debated.
OL,12,F"But as time and debate has worn on,
OL,13,Fit has become increasingly clear that
OL,14,Fthis Bill is unsafe and unworkable.
OL,16,F"The possibility for coercion of
OL,17,Fvulnerable individuals cannot be
OL,18,Fignored, and nor can the ramifications
OL,19,Ffor healthcare staff who will not be
OL,20,Fprotected.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773115421
OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill reaches final
OL,4,Cstage at Holyrood
OL,6,F"This is a monumental decision for
OL,7,FMSPs, made more difficult by the
OL,8,Fextent to which the Bill remains
OL,9,Funworkable."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]
